Usage: setDontUse [-help] [-hinst <string> [-reset ]] { {<cellName> <value>} | {-reset } }

-help               # Prints out the command usage
<cellName>          # cell name  (string, optional)
<value>             # value true/false  (string, optional)
-hinst <string>     # hierarchy instance name (string, optional)
-reset              # reset constraints attached to the module and submodules
                    # (bool, optional)